Notes: WIAC Championship - Final...UWO wins league tournament for the third straight
year, sixth time in eight seasons and seventh time overall...Porath, who
during the game became the 22nd UWO player to reach 1,000 career points, had
82 points & 33 rebounds in this year's three WIAC tournament games.
